    {
      "id": "b73f9e60-fc2b-4090-9706-01b0448669a8",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Calculer la division euclidienne de $X^5+1$ par $X^4-2 X^3+X^2$.",
        "html": "<p>Calculer la division euclidienne de <span\nclass=\"math inline\">\\(X^5+1\\)</span> par <span\nclass=\"math inline\">\\(X^4-2 X^3+X^2\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "d748d4a0-6688-40ac-9840-569e7a857a25",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "$$\nX^5+1=(X+2) \\cdot\\left(X^4-2 X^3+X^2\\right)+3 X^3-2 X^2+1\n$$",
        "html": "<p><span class=\"math display\">\\[X^5+1=(X+2) \\cdot\\left(X^4-2\nX^3+X^2\\right)+3 X^3-2 X^2+1\\]</span></p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "dda8c0c2-bf1a-49ec-8209-5edb8b5f4386",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Factoriser dans $\\mathbb{R}[X]$ le polynôme $X^4-2 X^3+X^2$.",
        "html": "<p>Factoriser dans <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\mathbb{R}[X]\\)</span> le\npolynôme <span class=\"math inline\">\\(X^4-2 X^3+X^2\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "ea1f5046-04cd-47b0-8d47-155a7b4bb120",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "$$\nX^4-2 X^3+X^2=X^2 \\cdot\\left(X^2-2 X+1\\right)=X^2 \\cdot(X-1)^2\n$$",
        "html": "<p><span class=\"math display\">\\[X^4-2 X^3+X^2=X^2 \\cdot\\left(X^2-2\nX+1\\right)=X^2 \\cdot(X-1)^2\\]</span></p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "82e4c5d4-4375-4725-92b0-562c619682dd",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "On note $F(X)=\\frac{X^5+1}{X^4-2 X^3+X^2}$. Donner la forme de la décomposition en éléments simples de $F(X)$ dans $\\mathbb{R}(X)$.",
        "html": "<p>On note <span class=\"math inline\">\\(F(X)=\\frac{X^5+1}{X^4-2\nX^3+X^2}\\)</span>. Donner la forme de la décomposition en éléments\nsimples de <span class=\"math inline\">\\(F(X)\\)</span> dans <span\nclass=\"math inline\">\\(\\mathbb{R}(X)\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "2cb68ad6-fa17-4d3f-85fa-a50c3a4de516",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "$$\nF(X)=\\frac{X^5+1}{X^4-2 X^3+X^2}=\\frac{X^5+1}{X^2 \\cdot(X-1)^2}=X+2+\\frac{A}{X}+\\frac{B}{X^2}+\\frac{C}{(X-1)}+\\frac{D}{(X-1)^2}\n$$",
        "html": "<p><span class=\"math display\">\\[F(X)=\\frac{X^5+1}{X^4-2\nX^3+X^2}=\\frac{X^5+1}{X^2\n\\cdot(X-1)^2}=X+2+\\frac{A}{X}+\\frac{B}{X^2}+\\frac{C}{(X-1)}+\\frac{D}{(X-1)^2}\\]</span></p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "1e70daa1-cc5b-4c7d-bf6b-b29d5d25aac4",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Calculer $\\lim\\limits_{X \\rightarrow 0}\\left(X^2 \\cdot F(X)\\right)$",
        "html": "<p>Calculer <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\lim\\limits_{X \\rightarrow\n0}\\left(X^2 \\cdot F(X)\\right)\\)</span></p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "d0b61881-3275-4693-bde0-79cf808241cb",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "$$\n\\begin{aligned}\n\t\\lim _{X \\rightarrow 0}\\left(X^2 \\cdot F(X)\\right) & =\\lim _{X \\rightarrow 0} \\frac{X^2 \\cdot\\left(X^5+1\\right)}{X^2 \\cdot(X-1)^2}=1 \\\\\n\t& =\\lim _{X \\rightarrow 0} X^2 \\cdot\\left[X+2+\\frac{A}{X}+\\frac{B}{X^2}+\\frac{C}{(X-1)}+\\frac{D}{(X-1)^2}\\right]=B\n\\end{aligned}\n$$",
        "html": "<p><span class=\"math display\">\\[\\begin{aligned}\n    \\lim _{X \\rightarrow 0}\\left(X^2 \\cdot F(X)\\right) &amp; =\\lim _{X\n\\rightarrow 0} \\frac{X^2 \\cdot\\left(X^5+1\\right)}{X^2 \\cdot(X-1)^2}=1 \\\\\n    &amp; =\\lim _{X \\rightarrow 0} X^2\n\\cdot\\left[X+2+\\frac{A}{X}+\\frac{B}{X^2}+\\frac{C}{(X-1)}+\\frac{D}{(X-1)^2}\\right]=B\n\\end{aligned}\\]</span></p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "d9d72a5b-58e0-409b-b19d-0f11e0259e11",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Calculer $\\lim\\limits_{X \\rightarrow 1}\\left((X-1)^2 \\cdot F(X)\\right)$.",
        "html": "<p>Calculer <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\lim\\limits_{X \\rightarrow\n1}\\left((X-1)^2 \\cdot F(X)\\right)\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "623ec22c-c235-43b9-b63b-04b4fd061027",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "$$\n\\begin{aligned}\n\t\\lim _{X \\rightarrow 1}\\left((X-1)^2 \\cdot F(X)\\right) & =\\lim _{X \\rightarrow 1} \\frac{(X A)^2 \\cdot\\left(X^5+1\\right)}{X^2 \\cdot(X-1)^2}=2 \\\\\n\t& =\\lim _{X \\rightarrow 1}(X-1)^2 \\cdot\\left[X+2+\\frac{A}{X}+\\frac{B}{X^2}+\\frac{C}{(X-1)}+\\frac{D}{(X-1)^2}\\right]=D\n\\end{aligned}\n$$",
        "html": "<p><span class=\"math display\">\\[\\begin{aligned}\n    \\lim _{X \\rightarrow 1}\\left((X-1)^2 \\cdot F(X)\\right) &amp; =\\lim\n_{X \\rightarrow 1} \\frac{(X A)^2 \\cdot\\left(X^5+1\\right)}{X^2\n\\cdot(X-1)^2}=2 \\\\\n    &amp; =\\lim _{X \\rightarrow 1}(X-1)^2\n\\cdot\\left[X+2+\\frac{A}{X}+\\frac{B}{X^2}+\\frac{C}{(X-1)}+\\frac{D}{(X-1)^2}\\right]=D\n\\end{aligned}\\]</span></p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "2148cf5b-daad-4605-9317-9cd95ad5b650",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Calculer $F(-1)$ et $F(2)$ de deux façons différentes.",
        "html": "<p>Calculer <span class=\"math inline\">\\(F(-1)\\)</span> et <span\nclass=\"math inline\">\\(F(2)\\)</span> de deux façons différentes.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "1d6d15a5-bfd4-497d-a6ca-c0237714225c",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "$$\n\\begin{aligned}\n\t& F(-1)=\\frac{(-1)^5+1}{(-1)^2 \\cdot(-1-1)^2}=0 \\\\\n\t&=-1+2+\\frac{A}{-1}+\\frac{1}{(-1)^2}+\\frac{C}{(-1-1)}+\\frac{2}{(-1-1)^2}=2-A-\\frac{C}{2}+\\frac{1}{2} \\\\\n\t& \\Rightarrow 2 A+C=5 \\\\\n\t& F(2)=\\frac{(2)^5+1}{(2)^2 \\cdot(2-1)^2}=\\frac{33}{4} \\\\\n\t&=2+2+\\frac{A}{2}+\\frac{1}{(2)^2}+\\frac{C}{(2-1)}+\\frac{2}{(2-1)^2}=4+\\frac{A}{2}+\\frac{1}{4}+C+2 \\\\\n\t& \\Rightarrow A+2 C=4 \\\\\n\t&\\left\\{\\begin{array} { l } \n\t\t{ 2 A + C = 5 } \\\\\n\t\t{ A + 2 C = 4 }\n\t\\end{array} \\Leftrightarrow \\left\\{\\begin{array}{l}\n\t\tA=2 \\\\\n\t\tC=1\n\t\\end{array}\\right.\\right.\n\\end{aligned}\n$$",
        "html": "<p><span class=\"math display\">\\[\\begin{aligned}\n    &amp; F(-1)=\\frac{(-1)^5+1}{(-1)^2 \\cdot(-1-1)^2}=0 \\\\\n    &amp;=-1+2+\\frac{A}{-1}+\\frac{1}{(-1)^2}+\\frac{C}{(-1-1)}+\\frac{2}{(-1-1)^2}=2-A-\\frac{C}{2}+\\frac{1}{2}\n\\\\\n    &amp; \\Rightarrow 2 A+C=5 \\\\\n    &amp; F(2)=\\frac{(2)^5+1}{(2)^2 \\cdot(2-1)^2}=\\frac{33}{4} \\\\\n    &amp;=2+2+\\frac{A}{2}+\\frac{1}{(2)^2}+\\frac{C}{(2-1)}+\\frac{2}{(2-1)^2}=4+\\frac{A}{2}+\\frac{1}{4}+C+2\n\\\\\n    &amp; \\Rightarrow A+2 C=4 \\\\\n    &amp;\\left\\{\\begin{array} { l }\n        { 2 A + C = 5 } \\\\\n        { A + 2 C = 4 }\n    \\end{array} \\Leftrightarrow \\left\\{\\begin{array}{l}\n        A=2 \\\\\n        C=1\n    \\end{array}\\right.\\right.\n\\end{aligned}\\]</span></p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
